For each event, provide:
1. A realistic title
2. An appropriate duration in minutes based on the event type

Consider realistic time durations:
- Gym/fitness: 60-180 minutes
- Medical appointments: 30-90 minutes
- Business meetings: 30-120 minutes
- Study sessions: 60-180 minutes
- Work appointments: 30-90 minutes
- Social activities: 60-180 minutes
- Quick tasks: 15-45 minutes
- Dental appointments: 30-60 minutes
- Therapy sessions: 45-90 minutes
- Phone calls: 15-30 minutes
- Lunch/coffee breaks: 30-60 minutes
- Exercise classes: 60-120 minutes
- Project work: 90-180 minutes
- Team sync: 30-60 minutes

Return only a JSON array of objects with this format:
[
  {"title": "Event Title", "duration": 60},
  {"title": "Another Event", "duration": 90}
]
`;

